Title: Ubuntu 19.04 Release Party
Book Description: Come celebrate the release of the latest Ubuntu 19.04 release- code-named 'Disco Dingo'. We'll meet in the bar area and raise a glass to mark the occasion.

Title: BOF: Installing Open Source Software is Too Complicated Now
Book Description: Birds of a Feather: Have you ever had an open source software install fail because the documentation is outdated and the versions of supporting packages have all changed? Let's talk about this difficult problem!
